getValidField

public static java.lang.reflect.Field[] getValidField(java.lang.Object obj,
                                                      CodecParameter codecParam)
Get valid object fields.

参数：
obj - Target object.
codecParam - Codec parameter.
返回：
If field 'fieldSequence' exists, return the fields specify by 'fieldSequence'. Otherwise return object fields deeply without the class flaged by CodecType.
